variable januso
NUMBER 2891
NAME Janus' Wall
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START  
You are standing on a plain of cobbled stone. Before you is an enormous stone
wall that extends for as far as you can see to your left and right. The wall 
towers above you, casting a deep shadow all around. Set in the wall directly 
in front of you is Janus.
*DESCRIPTION_END 
ITEM 0 420
ITEM 1 66 VAl2=206 VAL3=2891 UNLOCKED
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0 
The wall is formed of enormous granite blocks, an incomprehensible 
feat of masonry.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Before you stands a large door and frame crafted of veined marble. Staring
impassively from the top of the frame is a stone face carved of alabaster.
You can see no means to open the door.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB CLIMB 0
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER You look around for a handhold, but the joints between the stones are 
ECHO PLAYER nearly seamless, and the surface of the rock is polished smooth.
ECHO OTHERS %N approaches the wall as if %S is going to climb it, but steps back 
ECHO OTHERS a moment later with furrowed brow.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL 0
CLEARVERB
ECHO ALL From far overhead, you hear the grinding of an enormous stone...
ECHO ALL then a sudden rush of wind...
ECHO PLAYER You are squashed flat by a piece of wall!
ECHO OTHERS %P is squashed flat by a piece of wall!
KILL PLAYER
NEWITEM 2 44 ADJ1=451
ENDIF 
IFPREVERB OPEN 1
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER The door refuses to budge at even your most insistent pushing and pulling.
ECHO OTHERS %N attempts to open Janus' door with no success.
ENDIF
ifentry -1
plrevent 1
contplrevent
add januso 1
equal dummy1 januso
mod dummy1 8
add dummy1 1
ifvar dummy1 = 1
echo player [Page from Scottmart]: Hiya Scott, baby.
endif
ifvar dummy1 = 2
echo player [Page from Janus]: How's it hangin', surfer dude?.
endif
ifvar dummy1 = 3
echo player [Page from Hollister]: Are you using my name in vain?
endif
ifvar dummy1 = 4
echo player [Page from Janus]: Hiya Scott, baby.
endif
ifvar dummy1 = 5
echo player [Page from Scottmart]: How's it hangin', surfer dude?.
endif
ifvar dummy1 = 6
echo player [From Janus]: Hey, Scotty, how's it hangin'?
endif
ifvar dummy1 = 7
plrevent 1
contplrevent
echo player [Page from Scottmart]: Who are you?
endif
ifvar dummy1 = 8
plrevent 1
contplrevent
echo player [Page from FordPinto]: Hiya Scotty, baby.
plrevent 1
contplrevent
echo player [Page from Kremlin]: hiya Scotty Baby
plrevent 1
contplrevent
echo player [Page from Snartborg]: Hiya Scott baby
plrevent 1
contplrevent
echo player [Page from Siphilid]: Heya Scott, baby!!!!
plrevent 2
contplrevent
echo player [Page from Growbaby]: Hiya Scott baby.
endif
endif


